div
  pagination(total-items="totalItems"
      ng-model="currentPage"
      num-pages="numPages"
      ng-change="pageChanged()"
      max-size="maxSize"
      rotate="false"
      boundary-links="true"
      previous-text!="&lsaquo;"
      next-text!="&rsaquo;"
      first-text!="&laquo;"
      last-text!="&raquo;")
  pre
    | The selected page no: {{currentPage}} / {{numPages}}
